title: Janes F-15 & Manual & Patch
description:
Jane's F-15 Game:
================

This torrent gathers the following:

1) Jane's F-15 game ISO file;
2) Manual PDF files (both Casual and Expert manuals), from http://www.replacementdocs.com
3) Latest patch

Instructions:

1) Burn the ISO on a CD (or use a ISO mounting tool such as Daemon Tools);
2) Install the game;
3) Apply the patch;
4) Refer to manual

And you are done!

Enjoy :-)
